Sub-Fork version 1.00
=====================

Sub::Fork - Running subroutines in forked process 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IPC::Shareable  v0.6

